<section sectnbr = "9E">
<servcat sctnbr = "09" scnbr = "05">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A9506019" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Power Door Mirror On-Vehicle Inspection
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A9506019001">
<title>
Power Door Mirror Motor
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove sash bracket inner garnish and front door trim. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A9506009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect power door mirror connector (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check battery terminals to power door mirror connector as shown in the following table and check operation of power door mirror motor.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified in the following operation, replace power door mirror.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<title>
Power door mirror motor operation
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B950003.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.376mm" ver = "01" gw = "211" gh = "123"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B950004.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "75.297mm" ver = "01" gw = "207" gh = "197"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
